{"word":"Dog","slug":"dog","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dog</b> Price of, not to be brought into the sanctuary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=18'>Deu 23:18</a><br/> Shepherd dogs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=30&verse=1'>Job 30:1</a><br/> Habits of:<br/> - Licking blood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=19'>1Ki 21:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=38'>1Ki 22:38</a> <br/> - Licking sores<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=21'>Luk 16:21</a> <br/> - Returns to his vomit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=26&verse=11'>Pro 26:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=22'>2Pe 2:22</a> <br/> - Lapping of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=5'>Jdg 7:5</a> <br/> - Dumb and sleeping<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=56&verse=11'>Isa 56:11</a> <br/> Greyhound<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=31'>Pro 30:31</a><br/> Epithet of contempt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=43'>1Sa 17:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=24&verse=14'>1Sa 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=8'>2Sa 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=9&verse=8'>2Sa 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Sa 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=13'>2Ki 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=56&verse=11'>Isa 56:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=26'>Mat 15:26</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=2'>Phi 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=22&verse=15'>Rev 22:15</a>"}]}